据库（插件）\r\n4.保存 ssh 密钥，监听系统的 ssh 链接自动调起密钥选择界面（插件）\r\n5.通过加密协议，监听浏览器密码请求，将密码传输到浏览器（并非浏览器直接读取数据库文件，依然是客户端解锁）（插件）\r\n6.支持通用的 6 位、steam 的 5 位两步验证器（插件）\r\n7.密码历史版本\r\n8.防读内存，防读剪贴板，防键盘记录器（双通道混淆）\r\n\r\nBitwarden 能实现以上功能？或有其他优点吗？","content_rendered":"诸位大佬们，用过的说下这俩哪个更好呢？是否需要把 Keepass 淘汰迁移到 Bitwarden ？<br /><br />目前 Keepass 我比较中意的功能：<br />1.webdav 同步<br />2.全平台<br />3.windows hello 指纹解锁数据库（插件）<br />4.保存 ssh 密钥，监听系统的 ssh 链接自动调起密钥选择界面（插件）<br />5.通过加密协议，监听浏览器密码请求，将密码传输到浏览器（并非浏览器直接读取数据库文件，依然是客户端解锁）（插件）<br />6.支持通用的 6 位、steam 的 5 位两步验证器（插件）<br />7.密码历史版本<br />8.防读内存，防读剪贴板，防键盘记录器（双通道混淆）<br /><br />Bitwarden 能实现以上功能？或有其他优点吗？","last_modified":1668043417,"replies":17,"id":894022},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_large.png?m=1630576655","name":"hardware","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_normal.png?m=1630576655","title":"硬件","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware","topics":4730,"footer":"","header":"硬件发烧友的讨论节点","title_alternative":"Hardware","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655","stars":2087,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":52,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":561400,"username":"tool2d","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tool2d","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9e4b/c61b/561400_mini.png?m=1667209262","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9e4b/c61b/561400_normal.png?m=1667209262","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9e4b/c61b/561400_large.png?m=1667209262","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9e4b/c61b/561400_xlarge.png?m=1667209262","created":1636525139,"last_modified":1667209262},"last_reply_by":"lingex","last_touched":1668057464,"title":"CPU 坏了，能修吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894068","created":1668048887,"deleted":0,"content":"用了 3 年的 4 代 Intel CPU ，上周突然挂了。具体症状是进 Windows 10 系统会蓝屏自动重启，但是用安全模式进入，又完全没问题。\r\n\r\n一开始没想到 CPU 会坏，换了一块硬盘，拔了多余内存条，拔了显卡都无效，最后发现是 CPU 故障，淘宝买了同款 CPU, 换上就能解决问题。\r\n\r\n下面是坏 CPU 的照片，肉眼看不出有什么明显问题啊？\r\n\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/VeGcgRl.jpg","content_rendered":"用了 3 年的 4 代 Intel CPU ，上周突然挂了。具体症状是进 Windows 10 系统会蓝屏自动重启，但是用安全模式进入，又完全没问题。<br /><br />一开始没想到 CPU 会坏，换了一块硬盘，拔了多余内存条，拔了显卡都无效，最后发现是 CPU 故障，淘宝买了同款 CPU, 换上就能解决问题。<br /><br />下面是坏 CPU 的照片，肉眼看不出有什么明显问题啊？<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/VeGcgRl.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VeGcgRl.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a>","last_modified":1668048887,"replies":15,"id":894068},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_large.png?m=1630576655","name":"hardware","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_normal.png?m=1630576655","title":"硬件","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware","topics":4730,"footer":"","header":"硬件发烧友的讨论节点","title_alternative":"Hardware","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655","stars":2087,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":52,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":279175,"username":"mrzx","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mrzx","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2b7c/af18/279175_mini.png?m=1661750224","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2b7c/af18/279175_normal.png?m=1661750224","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2b7c/af18/279175_large.png?m=1661750224","created":1514963125,"last_modified":1661750224},"last_reply_by":"mrzx","last_touched":1668054290,"title":"PC 机全固态硬盘，除系统盘用 NTFS 格式之外。其他盘符可否采用 exfat?","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894064","created":1668047687,"deleted":0,"content":"因为个人电脑，不需要权限管理，也不需要数据恢复（家里有专门的 nas 保存重要数据）。\r\n\r\n但不清楚 exfat 还有什么隐性缺陷？网上搜的一堆只讲优点，唯一的缺点就是缺乏日志，对数据恢复性比较差。\r\n\r\n细想一下，固态不存在所谓的坏块啊。。。根本不会造成数据放在那好好的，突然数据就损坏了，要损坏，固态就全部坏掉。\r\n\r\n\r\n你们谁有长期在固态硬盘上使用 exfat 的体验啊？","content_rendered":"<p>因为个人电脑，不需要权限管理，也不需要数据恢复（家里有专门的 nas 保存重要数据）。</p>\n<p>但不清楚 exfat 还有什么隐性缺陷？网上搜的一堆只讲优点，唯一的缺点就是缺乏日志，对数据恢复性比较差。</p>\n<p>细想一下，固态不存在所谓的坏块啊。。。根本不会造成数据放在那好好的，突然数据就损坏了，要损坏，固态就全部坏掉。</p>\n<p>你们谁有长期在固态硬盘上使用 exfat 的体验啊？</p>\n","last_modified":1668047687,"replies":15,"id":894064},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":192723,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3610,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":343565,"username":"kongyian","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kongyian","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c992/fee6/343565_mini.png?m=1570790171","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c992/fee6/343565_normal.png?m=1570790171","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c992/fee6/343565_large.png?m=1570790171","created":1534929436,"last_modified":1570790171},"last_reply_by":"Cavolo","last_touched":1668052411,"title":"给老妈换个 2k 左右的安卓手机，求推荐","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894055","created":1668047046,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1668047046,"replies":14,"id":894055},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":192723,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3610,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":128480,"username":"doomzc","url